list.name: Changes
list.comment: I redid the main file, and moved most of the simulation code to simulation.py. main.py is still the runnable file. Let me know if you have any questions about what stuff does, I tried to use lots of comments lol. If you'd like to I think it would be good to make all the animals inherit from a main class too, and then have Carnivore and Herbivore classes that inherit and override certain methods.
